SQL: SELECT "customer"."c_birth_year", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_page"."wp_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk"  WHERE ("customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate" = 8000 OR CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%70%00%' OR CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%9500%') AND CAST("customer"."c_salutation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%D%r.%' AND CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_net_paid" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.%0%' AND ("customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" IN ('Unknown') OR CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Lo%w%' OR "customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" IN ('High Risk')) AND "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_count" = 5 GROUP BY "customer"."c_birth_year" ORDER BY "customer"."c_birth_year";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk"  WHERE CAST("call_center"."cc_hours" AS varchar) LIKE '%8A%M-4PM%';

SELECT "warehouse"."w_street_name", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "warehouse" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE "warehouse"."w_gmt_offset" = -6.00 AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%4%.0%' GROUP BY "warehouse"."w_street_name" ORDER BY "warehouse"."w_street_name";

SELECT "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales"  WHERE "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk" IN (5139, 6698, 3877, 1901, 7052, 2285, 1941, 6656, 4872, 893, 5850, 3954, 4110) AND "store_sales"."ss_sold_date_sk" = 2452604 AND CAST("store_sales"."ss_ext_tax" AS varchar) LIKE '%0%.0%' GROUP BY "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk" ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "ship_mode" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk"  WHERE ("ship_mode"."sm_type" = 'EXPRESS' OR (CAST("ship_mode"."sm_code" AS varchar) LIKE '%AIR%' AND "ship_mode"."sm_type" != 'LIBRARY')) AND "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" IN (4, 3, 2, 1, 5) AND (CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%13.0%' OR ("catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" != 15 AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%13.0%'));

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_order_number" = "web_returns"."wr_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("item"."i_manager_id" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%8.0%' AND CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%20%';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returning_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "web_returns"."wr_returned_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_returns"."wr_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_birth_month" AS varchar) LIKE '%10.0%' AND "date_dim"."d_fy_year" = 1940 AND CAST("customer"."c_birth_day" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%16.0%' AND CAST("item"."i_rec_end_date" AS varchar) LIKE '%1999-10-27%' AND CAST("time_dim"."t_sub_shift" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%evening%';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "customer"."c_current_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "customer"."c_current_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk"  WHERE "customer"."c_last_name" = 'Jones';

SELECT "store"."s_market_manager", "store"."s_rec_end_date", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "store_returns"."sr_store_sk" = "store"."s_store_sk"  WHERE "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" != 2452301 AND "store"."s_state" IN ('SD', 'TN', 'AL') AND (CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_amt" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.%0%' OR CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_amt" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%') AND ("store"."s_street_type" != 'Street' OR "store"."s_street_type" != 'Ave' OR CAST("store"."s_street_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RD%') GROUP BY "store"."s_market_manager", "store"."s_rec_end_date" ORDER BY "store"."s_market_manager", "store"."s_rec_end_date";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_following_holiday", "customer"."c_birth_month", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_page"."wp_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk"  WHERE "customer"."c_birth_month" IN (12, 2, 3) AND "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk" IN (101, 138, 73, 132, 42, 169, 155, 154, 11, 124, 125, 205, 51, 69, 200, 54, 29) AND "date_dim"."d_fy_year" IN (1972) AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" = 2451913 GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_following_holiday", "customer"."c_birth_month" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_following_holiday", "customer"."c_birth_month";

SELECT "customer"."c_birth_month", "web_site"."web_company_name", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_site" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_site"."web_close_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_dom" IN (8, 7, 1, 16, 19, 28, 27, 22, 18, 9, 3, 15) AND CAST("web_site"."web_site_id" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AAAAAAA%AKBAAAAAA%' AND "customer"."c_birth_country" IS NOT NULL GROUP BY "customer"."c_birth_month", "web_site"."web_company_name" ORDER BY "customer"."c_birth_month", "web_site"."web_company_name";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "warehouse"  WHERE "warehouse"."w_state" IN ('OH');

SELECT "date_dim"."d_week_seq", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "promotion" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "promotion"."p_end_date_sk"  WHERE ("date_dim"."d_dom" = 1 OR ("date_dim"."d_current_week" != 'N' AND CAST("date_dim"."d_dom" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%2%1%')) AND (CAST("call_center"."cc_tax_percentage" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.12%' OR CAST("call_center"."cc_tax_percentage" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.1%1%') GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_week_seq" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_week_seq";

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_site" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_site"."web_open_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_sold_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE "web_site"."web_suite_number" IN ('Suite 210', 'Suite Q', 'Suite 370', 'Suite D', 'Suite 460', 'Suite 440', 'Suite U', 'Suite 470', 'Suite G', 'Suite J', 'Suite T', 'Suite 30', 'Suite 260') AND "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" IN (86, 245, 259, 11, 317, 265, 76, 138, 292, 140, 203, 189, 35, 197, 361, 127, 225, 73) AND "date_dim"."d_weekend" IN ('N') GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "call_center" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_closed_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_addr_sk"  WHERE "web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" = 14 AND "date_dim"."d_fy_year" IN (1956, 1980, 1908, 2020) AND "date_dim"."d_current_week" != 'N';

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returned_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_reason_sk" IN (28, 16, 8, 29, 4, 17, 30, 20, 32, 6, 11) AND CAST("time_dim"."t_minute" AS varchar) LIKE '%12%' AND "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" != 3959;

SELECT "reason"."r_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "reason"  WHERE "reason"."r_reason_desc" IN ('Did not like the color', 'reason 29', 'reason 31', 'Package was damaged', 'Did not get it on time', 'reason 33', 'Did not like the model', 'reason 34', 'reason 27') AND "reason"."r_reason_desc" IN ('Package was damaged', 'Did not like the model', 'reason 37', 'Did not fit', 'Does not work with a product that I have', 'reason 31', 'reason 23', 'Not the product that was ordred', 'No service location in my area', 'reason 32', 'reason 33', 'Did not like the color', 'reason 34', 'reason 27') AND "reason"."r_reason_id" IN ('AAAAAAAACBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAANBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAMAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADCAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAIBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAOAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAPAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAALAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAMBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAFAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAKAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAJAAAAAAA') AND "reason"."r_reason_sk" = 18 GROUP BY "reason"."r_reason_sk" ORDER BY "reason"."r_reason_sk";

SELECT "store"."s_store_name", "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "store"."s_store_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_store_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "store_returns"."sr_ticket_number" = "store_sales"."ss_ticket_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "item" ON "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" = "item"."i_item_sk"  WHERE "store"."s_division_name" = 'Unknown' AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_return_amt_inc_tax" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.%0%' AND CAST("item"."i_rec_end_date" AS varchar) LIKE '%2000-10-26%' GROUP BY "store"."s_store_name", "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk" ORDER BY "store"."s_store_name", "store_returns"."sr_reason_sk";
SELECT "item"."i_size", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "item"  WHERE "item"."i_size" = 'small' AND "item"."i_brand_id" != 2002001 GROUP BY "item"."i_size" ORDER BY "item"."i_size";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_day", "call_center"."cc_market_manager", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "ship_mode" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" = "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "call_center" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" = "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "call_center"."cc_open_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_item_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%1%.0%' AND "ship_mode"."sm_type" IN ('TWO DAY', 'EXPRESS') AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_return_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%35%.0%' GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_current_day", "call_center"."cc_market_manager" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_current_day", "call_center"."cc_market_manager";

SELECT "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_page"."wp_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returning_customer_sk"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" IN (4507, 2800, 362, 4970, 4020, 135, 843, 6170, 1408) GROUP BY "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk" ORDER BY "web_page"."wp_creation_date_sk";

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" = "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "web_returns"."wr_returned_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_bill_addr_sk"  WHERE CAST("customer_address"."ca_county" AS varchar) LIKE '%city%' AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" != 2451546 GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store"."s_closed_date_sk"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_dow" = 5 AND "store"."s_hours" = '8AM-8AM';

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_item_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_item_sk"  WHERE CAST("web_sales"."ws_ext_tax" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%21%.0%' AND "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" IN (18, 14, 13, 9, 2, 7, 1, 5, 6) GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE "customer_address"."ca_street_type" != 'Way';

SELECT "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "promotion" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "promotion"."p_promo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk"  WHERE CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_education_status" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Secondary%' AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_ext_sales_price" AS varchar) LIKE '%0%.0%' AND "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" IN (86, 245, 361, 176, 259, 197, 189, 76, 203, 317, 73, 265, 56, 292, 11) GROUP BY "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk" ORDER BY "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales"  WHERE CAST("web_sales"."ws_warehouse_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%3.0%' AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%13.0%' AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" IS NOT NULL;

SELECT "ship_mode"."sm_carrier", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "ship_mode" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" = "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returned_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_hdemo_sk"  WHERE "time_dim"."t_hour" = 18 AND "store_returns"."sr_store_sk" IN (86, 8, 50, 40, 20, 91, 31, 34, 73, 61, 13, 80, 92, 52, 25, 67, 22, 43) GROUP BY "ship_mode"."sm_carrier" ORDER BY "ship_mode"."sm_carrier";

SELECT "customer_address"."ca_location_type", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_address"  WHERE CAST("customer_address"."ca_county" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%cit%y%' GROUP BY "customer_address"."ca_location_type" ORDER BY "customer_address"."ca_location_type";
SELECT "date_dim"."d_dow", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim"  GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_dow" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_dow";

SELECT "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" != 3 AND "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" != 13 GROUP BY "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" ORDER BY "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk"  WHERE "customer"."c_birth_year" IN (1970, 1963, 1945, 1928, 1948, 1954, 1972) AND "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" != 15 AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk" IN (4020, 3081, 4164, 6170, 620, 7143, 5304, 4974, 135) AND "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk" = 2451276;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "catalog_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "time_dim" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_returned_time_sk" = "time_dim"."t_time_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_order_number" = "catalog_sales"."cs_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_returning_hdemo_sk"  WHERE "customer"."c_salutation" IN ('Sir', 'Mr.') AND ("catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" IN (3188, 3134, 5651, 6071, 593, 1178) OR (CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_return_ship_cost" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.%0%' AND "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" = 4985));

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "promotion" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "promotion"."p_promo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk"  WHERE "customer_demographics"."cd_marital_status" IN ('S') AND "promotion"."p_channel_radio" = 'N' AND "customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" != 'Good';

SELECT "promotion"."p_channel_catalog", "promotion"."p_purpose", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "promotion" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_sales" ON "promotion"."p_promo_sk" = "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk"  WHERE CAST("store_sales"."ss_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%56.%0%' AND "promotion"."p_promo_id" = 'AAAAAAAAFJAAAAAA' GROUP BY "promotion"."p_channel_catalog", "promotion"."p_purpose" ORDER BY "promotion"."p_channel_catalog", "promotion"."p_purpose";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_hdemo_sk"  WHERE CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%5%' AND "income_band"."ib_upper_bound" != 200000 AND CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%1%4%';

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_sales"."ws_bill_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk"  WHERE "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" IN (2451183, 2451547, 2451913) AND ("web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" IN (76, 361, 35, 127, 317, 292, 11, 189, 86, 197) OR ("web_sales"."ws_quantity" = 17 AND "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" = 225)) AND (CAST("customer_address"."ca_gmt_offset" AS varchar) LIKE '%-5.0%' OR CAST("customer_address"."ca_country" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%States%') AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_county" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Pa%rish%' GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_promo_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "ship_mode"  WHERE CAST("ship_mode"."sm_code" AS varchar) LIKE '%S%EA%' AND "ship_mode"."sm_type" = 'OVERNIGHT' AND (CAST("ship_mode"."sm_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%DAY%' OR "ship_mode"."sm_type" != 'NEXT DAY' OR "ship_mode"."sm_type" = 'REGULAR') AND "ship_mode"."sm_carrier" IN ('ORIENTAL', 'AIRBORNE', 'ZOUROS') AND "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_id" IN ('AAAAAAAANAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAJAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAHAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAIAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAFAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAADBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAABBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAEAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAPAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAACBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAALAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAABAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAMAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAEBAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAKAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAOAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAABAAAAAAA', 'AAAAAAAAGAAAAAAA');

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_returns"."wr_order_number" = "web_sales"."ws_order_number"  WHERE "web_sales"."ws_web_site_sk" != 9 GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk";

SELECT "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_returns" LEFT OUTER JOIN "reason" ON "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" = "reason"."r_reason_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "web_returns"."wr_order_number" = "web_sales"."ws_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_page" ON "web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" = "web_page"."wp_web_page_sk"  WHERE "reason"."r_reason_desc" != 'Did not like the warranty' GROUP BY "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" ORDER BY "web_returns"."wr_return_quantity";

SELECT "web_site"."web_rec_start_date", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_site" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_site"."web_open_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk"  WHERE CAST("web_site"."web_mkt_desc" AS varchar) LIKE '%c%amp%' AND CAST("web_site"."web_street_number" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%8%41%' AND CAST("customer"."c_first_name" AS varchar) LIKE '%David%' AND ("customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk" IN (2449654, 2449269, 2450093, 2449267, 2450200, 2451286, 2451020, 2449038, 2450064, 2451976, 2452155, 2451115, 2449601, 2449807, 2451161, 2450780, 2449648) OR (CAST("customer"."c_birth_year" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%992.0%' AND "customer"."c_first_shipto_date_sk" = 2450093)) GROUP BY "web_site"."web_rec_start_date" ORDER BY "web_site"."web_rec_start_date";

SELECT "customer_address"."ca_gmt_offset", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_address" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "customer"."c_current_addr_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "web_sales"."ws_order_number" = "web_returns"."wr_order_number"  WHERE CAST("web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%19%.0%' GROUP BY "customer_address"."ca_gmt_offset" ORDER BY "customer_address"."ca_gmt_offset";

SELECT "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_count", "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer_demographics"  WHERE CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" AS varchar) LIKE '%Low%' AND "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count" = 6 GROUP BY "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_count", "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count" ORDER BY "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_count", "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "web_page"."wp_customer_sk" = "customer"."c_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_order_number" = "catalog_returns"."cr_order_number"  WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_returning_hdemo_sk" = 6054 AND "catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_hdemo_sk" = 4981 AND CAST("catalog_returns"."cr_call_center_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%4.%0%';

SELECT "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "inventory"  WHERE "inventory"."inv_quantity_on_hand" = 359 OR "inventory"."inv_quantity_on_hand" IN (812, 650, 359, 956, 635, 302, 305, 746, 247, 561, 224) OR "inventory"."inv_quantity_on_hand" IN (635, 139, 224, 595, 656, 302, 382, 247, 561, 858, 956) GROUP BY "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk" ORDER BY "inventory"."inv_warehouse_sk";

SELECT "store_sales"."ss_quantity", "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "store_sales" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "store_sales"."ss_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" = 20 AND CAST("store_sales"."ss_quantity" AS varchar) LIKE '%45.%0%' AND "household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" != 3 AND CAST("store_sales"."ss_coupon_amt" AS varchar) LIKE '%0%.0%' GROUP BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity", "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_quantity", "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_refunded_customer_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_demographics" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_cdemo_sk" = "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_cdemo_sk"  WHERE "web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" != 6 AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_return_quantity" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%18.0%' AND CAST("customer_demographics"."cd_purchase_estimate" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%7000%' AND "customer"."c_last_name" IN ('White', 'Robinson', 'Smith', 'Thomas', 'Jackson') AND "customer"."c_last_name" = 'Miller';

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "ship_mode" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "web_sales"."ws_ship_hdemo_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk"  WHERE CAST("ship_mode"."sm_code" AS varchar) LIKE '%S%URFACE%' AND ("household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" = 0 OR ("household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" IN (0, -1, 3, 1) AND CAST("household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count" AS varchar) LIKE '%-1%')) AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%10.0%' GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk";

SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_month", "date_dim"."d_dow", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "date_dim"  WHERE "date_dim"."d_current_quarter" != 'N' AND "date_dim"."d_current_week" = 'N' AND "date_dim"."d_weekend" IN ('Y') GROUP BY "date_dim"."d_current_month", "date_dim"."d_dow" ORDER BY "date_dim"."d_current_month", "date_dim"."d_dow";

SELECT "web_sales"."ws_quantity", "customer_address"."ca_street_type", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "income_band" LEFT OUTER JOIN "household_demographics" ON "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" = "household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_returns" ON "household_demographics"."hd_demo_sk" = "web_returns"."wr_refunded_hdemo_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer_address" ON "web_returns"."wr_returning_addr_sk" = "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "customer_address"."ca_address_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_bill_addr_sk"  WHERE CAST("household_demographics"."hd_income_band_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%1%2%' AND CAST("web_returns"."wr_reason_sk" AS varchar) LIKE '%4.%0%' AND CAST("customer_address"."ca_suite_number" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%Suite%' GROUP BY "web_sales"."ws_quantity", "customer_address"."ca_street_type" ORDER BY "web_sales"."ws_quantity", "customer_address"."ca_street_type";

SELECT "store"."s_store_id", "store"."s_division_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_page" LEFT OUTER JOIN "date_dim" ON "web_page"."wp_access_date_sk" = "date_dim"."d_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "web_sales" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "web_sales"."ws_sold_date_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store" ON "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = "store"."s_closed_date_sk"  WHERE "web_sales"."ws_web_page_sk" != 151 GROUP BY "store"."s_store_id", "store"."s_division_id" ORDER BY "store"."s_store_id", "store"."s_division_id";

SELECT "warehouse"."w_county", "ship_mode"."sm_contract", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "warehouse" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_sales" ON "warehouse"."w_warehouse_sk" = "catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" LEFT OUTER JOIN "catalog_returns" ON "catalog_sales"."cs_order_number" = "catalog_returns"."cr_order_number" LEFT OUTER JOIN "ship_mode" ON "catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk" = "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk"  WHERE "ship_mode"."sm_code" IN ('SURFACE', 'SEA') AND CAST("warehouse"."w_state" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%L%A%' AND "catalog_sales"."cs_warehouse_sk" IN (5, 4, 3, 2, 1) AND "catalog_returns"."cr_catalog_page_sk" IN (7946, 4011, 207, 6005, 7975, 5946, 4041, 4063) GROUP BY "warehouse"."w_county", "ship_mode"."sm_contract" ORDER BY "warehouse"."w_county", "ship_mode"."sm_contract";

SELECT "customer"."c_login", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "store_returns" ON "customer"."c_customer_sk" = "store_returns"."sr_customer_sk"  WHERE "store_returns"."sr_hdemo_sk" != 7151 AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_store_credit" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("store_returns"."sr_reason_sk" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%24%.0%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_login" ORDER BY "customer"."c_login";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "web_sales"  WHERE CAST("web_sales"."ws_sales_price" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%' AND CAST("web_sales"."ws_ext_tax" AS varchar) LIKE '%0.0%';
